room_title: Escape room "The Funeral Parlor" by The Key Haunted Escape Rooms in Indianapolis
room_description: You’ll never be late for this funeral… it’s been going on since 1952. Jebidiah Clayton’s spirit is angry, and for several reasons that you will discover while attending the service at the Hockaloogie Funeral Parlor. Help this poor guy come to terms with his life so that he may be free to continue his journey to the light.
